- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the topological structure of ecosystems and how it relates to the optimisation technique. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses evolutionary computing and optimisation techniques. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses self-organisation and scalability in the context of natural ecosystems.
